getLegType

public int getLegType()
Get the type of leg: LEGTYPE_UPWIND, LEGTYPE_DOWNWIND, LEGTYPE_REACHING or LEGTYPE_UNKNOWN.

Note that legtype isn't entered as part of the course defination, but calculated using the following logic:

  • First leg is considered an upwind leg
  • Leg +/- 22.5 degrees compared to first leg are also considered upwind
  • Legs 180 +/- 22.5 degress compared to the first leg are considered downwind
  • All other legs are considered reaching

    • Returns:
    the legType as an int
